Creation Date:23/01/2021
Author: Karthick

This project is to create docker volume and db container for flask application.

1. create docker volume
2. create docker network for app and mysql communication
3. pull docker mysql image and configure it with the volume and network created.
4.install dependencies
5. create requirment.txt file
6. build your application into image
7. run your image into existing db network to communicate with db container
6. commit for source control